{"type": "article", "id": 23451, "title": "木质饭盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-08T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164632XjLzIYZQgJBabkho.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个可携带的木质饭盒，它另配有不同型号的保温盒，相应的 Prepd App 提供健康食谱的意见，指导你购买食物。当你按照食谱准备时，就能得到相应的热能计算，方便减法人士控制饮食。木质的盖子滑动下来，也可作为吃饭的垫子。刀叉等餐具都带磁铁，以便更好地固定在饭盒里。产品目前还在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/prepd-pack-the-lunchbox-reimagined#/\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164630snweukM6O3vTzmAl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164631dDzugXj3BSRPGfiq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164631WMHxuRtosOqLZEIh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164631JSsFaLNChgZqW0xw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.57205882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}